{"tid":1062320,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《人中之龍》工作室製作人：不會讓審判之眼就這麼結束！！","createTime":"2019-03-15T04:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T03:28:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b82c898a5ee0c3ac28cf08fb3af2e31b1d138539","tid":1062320,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"在PS4遊戲《審判之眼：死神的遺言》中飾演黑道頭子羽村京平的日本演員「瀧正則」，12日驚傳吸食古柯鹼遭到警方逮捕。遊戲公司SEGA對此緊急宣布停止《審判之眼：死神的遺言》在亞洲區一切的銷售活動，目前包括在台灣PS Store在內的亞洲商店已經搜尋不到遊戲，連官網也全面下架。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F67.jpg&h=2678ceba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 目前在PS商店已經找不到《審判之眼》。（圖／翻攝自PS商店）</span></div><br />\n<br />\n由木村拓哉擔任主角的《審判之眼：死神的遺言》，去年12月推出後受到玩家正面評價，也有不少粉絲希望能繼續推出續作。不過發生如此重大的醜聞事件後，有許多粉絲相當擔心《審判之眼：死神的遺言》這個IP會不會就此結束。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1542860164-f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800-1392x783.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F1542860164-f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800-1392x783.jpg&h=448b2a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 受到演員吸毒事件影響，《審判之眼：死神的遺言》目前已在亞洲地區全面下架。（圖／SEGA提供）</span></div><br />\n<br />\n對此，SEGA 人中之龍工作室的製作人佐藤大輔13日就在推特上寫下：「不會就這麼結束，我不會讓它就這麼消失，<span style=\"color: red;\">總有一天一定會讓它復活。</span>」強硬的語氣也透露出人中之龍工作室對這個IP的重視。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F46.jpg&h=c424e6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 佐藤大輔在推特表示不會讓《審判之眼》就這麼結束。（圖／翻攝自推特）</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190314/3270617/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190314%2F3270617%2F&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=d536621e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190314/3270617/</a>"},{"pid":"1e103763aa9f14fba21541d5117f06bdfa4c8c59","tid":1062320,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"吸毒事件除了影響到已經發售的亞洲版外，《審判之眼：死神的遺言》本來預計在今年6月推出歐美版本，不過目前的下架策略僅針對亞洲地區，SEGA 尚未宣布歐美版未來是否會如期發售。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/15/123649_0c2b27b207db07a476ce752ea473821f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2F123649_0c2b27b207db07a476ce752ea473821f.png&h=fee18a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 香港實體店暫未受影響。（圖／翻攝自香港格價網）</span></div>"},{"pid":"fa3b66a78e535679fe86509543a46f599d3748f8","tid":1062320,"uid":84128,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"條友吸毒關隻game咩事？"},{"pid":"69b92e2db2042fcc49713db922eff0b92411e513","tid":1062320,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa3b66a78e535679fe86509543a46f599d3748f8","tid":1062320,"uid":84128,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"條友吸毒關隻game咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"連坐法"},{"pid":"52a2ed90b1631d55dbbe297891d55af9933a49e9","tid":1062320,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"唔明個角色關隻game咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90ae76397f19969477d01f105e88ed272a1d009","tid":1062320,"uid":32934,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"日本仔真係好戇鳩<br />\n不過可能搵第2個做. KEY返個頭, 錄過D聲再推出"},{"pid":"961774116637cf6c54ad49dc3947839f9c9c9a5